--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.2.2 (2020-12-20)
E: Modify 'textfile_collector' directory path to comply with Linux FHS

* Version 0.2.1 (2020-12-19)
E: Update sources after configuring APT repository

* Version 0.2.0 (2020-12-18)
F: Add APT repository 'buster-backports' (required for monit, opensmtpd, suricata)

* Version 0.1.1 (2020-12-15)
E: Add install_recommends parameter to package tasks

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-12-12)
F: Initial release
